[Bard, L. A., Bard, P. A., Owens, G. W., Hall, B. D. Retinal involvement in thoracic-pelvic-phalangeal dystrophy. Arch. Ophthal. 96: 278-281, 1978.]<br/>
[Hopper, M. St. C., Boultbee, J. E., Watson, A. R. Polyhydramnios associated with congenital pancreatic cysts and asphyxiating thoracic dysplasia: a case report. S. Afr. Med. J. 56: 32-33, 1979.]<br/></p>